EN: Their research found that the heart rate of patients with anxiety disorder increases when it reaches a certain threshold.

ZH: 为了保护隐私，他们设定了一个阈值，超过该阈值的数据将被匿名化处理。
EN: To protect privacy, they set a threshold, and data beyond that threshold will be anonymized.

